# mDNS Service Descriptor: _bart-collab._tcp

Service type used by bart to advertise and discover collab sessions on the local network.

## Service Type

  _bart-collab._tcp

## TXT Record Fields

| Key      | Description                                      | Example      |
|----------|--------------------------------------------------|--------------|
| code     | Short join code generated by the host            | ABC123       |
| peer     | Peer ID (UUID) of the advertising host           | <uuid>       |
| gitName  | git user.name of the host engineer (REQ-08)      | alice        |
| version  | Protocol version for compatibility checks        | 1            |

## Behaviour

- **Host** (`bart collab start`): advertises this service on the LAN with its join code embedded in the TXT record.
- **Joiner** (`bart collab join <code>`): browses for `_bart-collab._tcp` services and filters results by matching the `code` TXT field.
- Once the host is found, the joiner connects directly via TCP on the advertised port.

## Protocol Version

Current version: **1**
